  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Guarantee of Victims&#x2019; Representation through the Strengthening of the National General Attorney (PGN) to Contribute to the Processes of Truth, Justice, Reparation and Guarantees of Non-Repetition</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to improve society&apos;s confidence in the State and the peace process in Colombia by strengthening the institutional framework to guarantee the representation of the interests and rights of victims, making them key participants and promoting the conservation of historical memory. This includes the decongestion of cases being seen by the Special Jurisdiction for Peace in the Attorney General&apos;s Office and the design of strategies for guaranteeing the participation and representation of victims. Finally, it will promote the identification and management of the disciplinary processes for agents of the State in the context of the armed conflict.</narrative>
  </description>
